data.description: $5,000 in Closing Assistance!!!!This 3 bedroom 2 and a half bath, 2 car garage home feels more like a single family home than a townhome.  This home boasts upgrades galore!  A light and bright kitchen features sleek stainless steal appliances and a massive island perfect for entertaining.  Accents on details have been applied to every room.  A large fenced in yard is perfect for relaxing at the end of a tough day. For added security and convenience impact windows and doors.  Washer/Dryer is located upstairs for added convenience. Seller offering $5,000 in closing assistance  to buyer with accepted offer.
